Overdrive provides many advantages during battle, making it
a powerful asset if used correctly.
① Once activated, both members recover 30% of their HP
and EP, 30 of their CP, and are cured of all abnormalities.
② Three continuous turns are provided upon activation in
which all attacks and crafts are guaranteed to unbalance
③ All arts will be cast instantly.
The Overdrive gauge charges through dealing damage to
enemies and providing support to party members.
The gauge will also charge based on your tactical bonus
after battle. The higher the bonus, the more it will charge
While preserving Overdrive uses is a valid strategy,
utilizing it often is the key to swift, effective combat.
